s, hey, her says, do you want anything to eat? I says, please yourself, I says, I don't care whether I've had anything or nothing. Any road her brought me a cup of tea up, and - what was it - three or four - I think there was two sandwiches her brought up
,
 and I thought to myself - I don't - I says, who sent these up? Says, me - I - I've sneaked 'em up, her says, so - get 'em down you, her says, and - don't bang the plate the floor, she - any road, I thought myself well - I put the plate just under the bed
