e done nothing wrong. Oh well - come on and don't be so soft. Any road - when he come in he says - has her been down for anything eat? So - they said, no. So he says, oh - the best thing we'd better send her up, he says, if her's had now it'll all be full
 of wind. So I thought well d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11670890\charrsid15817332 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3500148\charrsid15817332 
