, I stopped in as I was. So he says, has - has her washed her? Mum says, no, not as I know to, her says, oh her's not been down since her went up. So - mother says, oh leave her, he says, don't have her - come down now again and wash her, her says, or her
 
won't go bed again. So one thing brought another but any road I didn't go downstairs again, I stopped in bed. I was there 'til next morning. I thought, oh I - he says, that'll learn you to come down when you've been sent for. Oh he says, I says, well I wa
s only standing there watching 'em. He says, well what did you see, nothing only dirt and dust. He says, a wonder you aren't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11670890\charrsid15817332 shocked}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
