rocks we used to have and - we liked 'em, and - was always frightened of getting it dirty. Used to come home - put an old 'un on. At night time. Then we used to - hadn't used to care what we did, see we could sit, squat down anywhere then. Used to think n
othing of sitting on the front steps. Then. Playing, playing bowler or - bat and ball.
