No, only there's one or two used go call for 'em, girls same as ourselves. We used to go to school with. No - lad - but - if he - father saw 
you talking to lads or - playing with 'em, he - used to shout you. But - him, can't you play - haven't you got no girls to play with instead of lads? Well makes no difference. Makes no Difference.
\par 
