re's some on 'em, they go past you and - they don't - won't as much - don't as much as speak to you. But - I mean it isn't as they don't know you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12523876 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3500148\charrsid15817332 
So really as far as you can remember in those days most of the kids just played happily together?
