 we had to go from our - where we lived we had to come about half an hour - half an hour's good walking to - Hanley baths. He used to say we - when we've gone there and bathed and back again he says - it's time for bed. But - of course they go from the sc
hools now don't they. Well we didn't. We hadn't used to go the baths like that. Not from schools.
