\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8026153 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3500148\charrsid15817332 
Oh in the street, I mean we didn't - 'course we could play in the street then, not no - didn't get shifted with the police same as they do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12523876 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3500148\charrsid15817332 Did you go to any theatres or concerts, music hall, cinemas?
